dcterms:description: The C-MAPSS dataset consists of multiple simulated engine run-to-failure trajectories, each containing sensor measurements and corresponding remaining useful life (RUL) labels. It is a widely used benchmark dataset for prognostics and health management research.
dcterms:title: C-MAPSS (Commercial Modular Aero-Propulsion System Simulation)
